<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Closest Bike Stations</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <script
        src="https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/js?key=AIzaSyALLWCBHM3rd9dx3Mhyqspj5-5q_Llm4cw&libraries=geometry,places"></script>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="app-container">
        <h1>Find Closest Bike Stations</h1>
        <p>Follow these simple steps to find the closest bike stations:</p>
        <ol>
            <li>Enter your destination in the search box.</li>
            <li>Click "Search" to find the nearest bike stations.</li>
            <li>Click on a bike station marker for directions.</li>
        </ol>

        <div class="search-container">
            <input id="destination" type="text" placeholder="Enter destination...">
            <button id="search">Search</button>
        </div>

        <div id="map" class="map-container" data-stations="<%= JSON.stringify(stations) %>"></div>
        <h2>Closest Stations:</h2>
        <ol id="closest-stations" class="stations-list"></ol>
    </div>
    <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>

</html>